snippet.title: Warframe | The Seven Crimes of Kullervo - Official Gameplay Trailer - Available Now
snippet.description:
Return to Duviri and delve into a sprawling new island dungeon where the tragic Warframe, Kullervo, awaits your redemption. This strange, floating prison obfuscates both Kullervo’s crimes as well as the mysterious (yet familiar) Warden who binds him under lock and key. Explore the prison’s cells to uncover the story of Kullervo’s misdeeds and wield the power of treachery through his trademark daggers and thirst for vengeance.

Enjoy new Customizations for your Fashion Frame like the Kullervo Usvah Helmet, Ahlto Syandana and the magnificent Vaenn Heavy Blade Skin. Or turbo-charge your Arsenal with the all-new Gauss Kresnik Collection, stunning Sentient-themed TennoGen designs, new Kaithe bundles and much, much more.

►► WHAT IS WARFRAME?

Join 70M+ registered players in Warframe, a cooperative, free-to-play third-person looter shooter set in a constantly evolving sci-fi universe. For more info, visit https://warframe.com. 

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlayWarframe/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayWarframe 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playwarframe/ 
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/warframe
